      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but then why is there so much pushback from huge groups of people then? if it's such a pragmatic and necessary tool to prevent a climate catastrophe, shouldn't the debate be more about how to build it safely/cheaply rather than debating whether to use it at all? feels like the opposition is just being unrealistic about the math.",
